Producer Bigfootinyourface and singer-songwriter Jazzz collaborate on a brilliant new 4-track project titled Silly Love Affair. Jazzz tells a story of two lovers who find and lose themselves in a world filled with yearning and passion. Bigfootinyourface provides a perfect canvas of experimental indie soul beats for Jazzz’ words and voice to come alive. The chemistry is palpable, the music is surreal, and Silly Love Affair leaves you with an unforgettable experience. Click on the following links to listen: Soundcloud Youtube Apple Music Spotify Read More: DMW Release Visuals For ‘Aje’ Read More: Nigerian Rock Artiste Nathmac Releases ‘Adesua’